Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.00,0:01:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『七鄉』的表面留下來的損傷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.37,0:01:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今都殘留下強大的妖力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.04,0:01:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手吧  如果還想要手的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.25,0:01:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是圓神…嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.56,0:01:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不會錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.14,0:01:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圓神還寄附在銀的身上嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.77,0:01:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀？啊 記得你們的關係不錯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.90,0:01:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.23,0:02:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有見面我怎麼知道啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.53,0:02:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說身體被附身已經2年
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.94,0:02:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很難想像靈魂還能殘留下來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.39,0:02:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 可能性不是0
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.68,0:02:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然這麼想是你的自由 但是太過執著…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.82,0:02:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.31,0:02:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.61,0:02:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.96,0:02:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗亞貝爾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.26,0:02:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.52,0:02:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳那身衣服 我差不多厭倦了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.44,0:02:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蹭蹭 得累 蹭得累 蹭蹭 蹭蹭 得累 蹭得累 蹭蹭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.87,0:02:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼歌？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.58,0:02:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,町歌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.36,0:02:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.48,0:02:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我作的 明天開始在鎮上播放
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.48,0:02:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.37,0:02:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也從internet登出的時候（歌曲不明）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.07,0:02:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,播放？在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.79,0:03:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點 快點起來不是更好嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.18,0:03:04.70,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,1000)}{\pos(442,320)}回首
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.54,0:03:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太漂亮了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.01,0:03:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  還不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.51,0:03:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.09,0:03:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時侯  小狗的意識已經完全消失了的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.87,0:03:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道我還不能完全使用這個身體嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.22,0:04:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好燙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.24,0:04:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不用幫也不要緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.65,0:04:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做這個還真辛苦呢~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.71,0:04:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  只不過是一些飯團和菜而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.50,0:04:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這些全是桃華做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.17,0:04:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 但是姬小姐想要吃出差地特產拉麵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.87,0:04:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以哥哥給她下了食物限制
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.47,0:04:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次是去秋田吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.56,0:04:26.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 那裡有妖怪遇到麻煩 讓過去接一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.26,0:04:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.02,0:04:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈 姬一直都叫我要弄成這大的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.87,0:04:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 這個不是很奇怪嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.11,0:04:36.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是可以整個放到嘴裡的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.09,0:04:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不放進去也可以的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.27,0:04:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.70,0:04:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在做什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.47,0:04:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口水一下子都出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.39,0:04:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是來幫忙的不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.45,0:04:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.57,0:04:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.12,0:04:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是炒麵 是姬的喜歡之物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.58,0:04:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  言葉為什麼擅自吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.63,0:05:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有吃 這個碳水化合物的結合
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.50,0:05:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明就吃了的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.65,0:05:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是在確認裡面東西而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.55,0:05:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不就是在準備吃不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.50,0:05:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種飯團誰會吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.41,0:05:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 這樣說對桃華很失禮的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.01,0:05:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.78,0:05:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炒麵什麼 真不敢想像
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.71,0:05:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和麵包和合  所以和白飯一起吃也很對味
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.80,0:05:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.41,0:05:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到飯團當然是配梅干了~對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.03,0:05:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的話 就配酒了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.36,0:05:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.58,0:05:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經是固定搭配了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.87,0:05:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有梅幹嗎？ 梅干
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.40,0:05:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.46,0:05:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬對梅干沒轍的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.20,0:05:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.81,0:05:32.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃不了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.36,0:05:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意外的小孩子一面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.28,0:05:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼呢 那種酸東西作為食物太奇怪了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.91,0:05:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.58,0:05:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.27,0:05:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不是很酸嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.16,0:05:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 完全不是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.11,0:05:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅干
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.82,0:05:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等 妳拿出什麼來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.22,0:05:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.55,0:05:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,髒死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.36,0:05:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來秋名呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.77,0:05:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是在事務所嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.10,0:06:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.94,0:06:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微有點濃了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.95,0:06:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.51,0:06:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 個人口味是各種各樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.09,0:06:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.60,0:06:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.51,0:06:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個炒麵飯團真好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.84,0:06:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言葉說這樣配不好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.44,0:06:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.75,0:06:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然很喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.93,0:06:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她舉止奇怪嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.57,0:06:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這麼說？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.82,0:06:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.75,0:06:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來有一點奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.04,0:06:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.25,0:06:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了什麼嗎？在區長那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.55,0:06:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.08,0:06:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵架了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.37,0:06:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.19,0:06:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是不明白那傢伙在想些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.75,0:06:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在意嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.32,0:06:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  以前就很在意了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.86,0:06:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.56,0:06:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬和秋名在交往嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.05,0:06:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.08,0:07:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…完全沒有的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.81,0:07:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼桃華在動搖呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.02,0:07:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 才沒有動搖呢 完全沒有關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.36,0:07:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是氣氛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.92,0:07:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣說是不是過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.63,0:07:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬和銀都是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.87,0:07:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.29,0:07:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.52,0:07:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖力稍微有些紊亂  這個身體在壓制我的妖力嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.52,0:07:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.61,0:07:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個就是町歌？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.82,0:07:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.82,0:07:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把這早中晚三次來回廣播？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.44,0:07:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.03,0:07:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當真？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.87,0:07:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當真
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.85,0:07:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要作好應對群眾上門抱怨的對策啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.09,0:07:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…唉？？？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.51,0:08:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是哥哥的份  姬的在這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.35,0:08:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做了多少？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.43,0:08:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是姬她這麼要求的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.09,0:08:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用理她也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.53,0:08:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐的健康狀態管理是我的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.42,0:08:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再吃小心跳不起來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.87,0:08:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣說不是很過分嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.26,0:08:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣只會呼呼的胖起來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.60,0:08:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起吃點心要好很多不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.19,0:08:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算吃 點心也夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.62,0:08:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好哦 久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.59,0:08:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等您很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.45,0:08:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 秋名 我的耳機
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.92,0:08:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.46,0:08:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.37,0:08:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前不是借給你了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.13,0:08:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.36,0:08:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就只有那一個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.17,0:08:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.87,0:08:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來借了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.97,0:08:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  快點快點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.27,0:08:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.27,0:08:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是想到要還給妳的 就放在這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.36,0:08:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.01,0:08:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.53,0:08:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向別人借的東西要好好對待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.74,0:08:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.88,0:08:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言葉 耳機借我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.44,0:08:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出差時要帶去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.07,0:08:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  2天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.23,0:08:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.25,0:08:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  我在卡拉OK的練習上要用的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.15,0:08:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼嘛 小氣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.47,0:08:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.58,0:08:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也只有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.91,0:08:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.60,0:08:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.40,0:09:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還留著呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.60,0:09:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「還」是什麼意思啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.09,0:09:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.81,0:09:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.90,0:09:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人啊 很重視回憶的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.55,0:09:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.30,0:09:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回憶是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.20,0:09:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個猴子貌似是很重要的東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.13,0:09:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.76,0:09:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是他們兩個人的 是三個人的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.23,0:09:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三人？還是一個人是？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.01,0:09:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒有放棄銀的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.06,0:09:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看起來像放棄了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.73,0:09:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒有放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.12,0:09:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我已經做好了覺悟 以前也說過的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.27,0:09:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百分之零的希望已經稱之不上是希望了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.45,0:09:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那時…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.07,0:09:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.17,0:10:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圓神大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.06,0:10:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別跟我說話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.78,0:10:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會錯 這個身體裡 銀的靈魂還留著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.72,0:10:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.42,0:10:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這兩年時間裡 好像都逃過了我的支配
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.04,0:10:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,值得稱讚啊 銀！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.16,0:11:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還差一點了 銀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.59,0:11:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還差的多 這樣很奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.48,0:11:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真囉嗦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.83,0:11:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才說沒可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.04,0:11:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別發牢騷了 快吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.99,0:11:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有3分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.43,0:11:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3分鐘？姬 妳帶著多少錢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.01,0:11:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.87,0:11:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事情別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.12,0:11:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.97,0:11:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「做不到怎麼辦」這樣的問題\N等到了毫無希望之時再想好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.56,0:11:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.29,0:11:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.22,0:11:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 銀 一盤3000日圓哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.24,0:11:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.20,0:11:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以認輸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.93,0:11:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.63,0:12:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.76,0:12:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼三人份 9000日圓我就要收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.45,0:12:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用一個星期的洗碗活來償還也是可以的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.39,0:12:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有1分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.99,0:12:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 銀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.19,0:12:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.22,0:12:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.34,0:12:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.73,0:12:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了 厲害 銀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.64,0:12:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.51,0:12:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.85,0:12:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要吐 千萬不要吐出來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.01,0:12:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.44,0:12:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出來了 面從鼻子裡出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.89,0:13:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.27,0:13:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.83,0:13:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要吐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.68,0:13:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 姬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.14,0:13:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.69,0:13:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說了嘛…是獎品啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.93,0:13:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.58,0:13:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們這麼的努力的在吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.16,0:13:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部吃下去的可是我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.52,0:13:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我的店弄的一團糟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.41,0:13:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來就應該是取消成績的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.05,0:13:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們就心存感激的接受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.37,0:13:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.50,0:13:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才說不要了的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.67,0:13:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也真是沒有辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.96,0:13:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 這個是秋名的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.45,0:13:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼是摀住耳朵不聽的姿勢(裝聾）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.82,0:13:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你不聽別人勸告
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.94,0:13:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實真正的意思並不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.86,0:13:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼姬就是蒙住眼睛不看的那個（裝瞎）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.67,0:13:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.59,0:13:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不聽別人的勸告 一個勁的往前衝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.48,0:13:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.69,0:14:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說我是閉上嘴巴不出聲的（裝啞巴）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.69,0:14:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fs20}注：みざるきかざるぃゎざ原是一個詞，是一種明哲保身的說法，不看不聽不\N說的意思，在這裡三人把他分段成3個詞組，分別表示三個人不同的個性特點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.50,0:14:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟銀很相佩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.98,0:14:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀本來就沒有什麼個性可言的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.70,0:14:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要說了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.89,0:14:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.88,0:14:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀 打算把我壓制住嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.63,0:14:42.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圓神大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.97,0:14:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.38,0:14:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一個銀的靈魂 我會突破結界的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.62,0:14:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圓神嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.22,0:15:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬出差去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.33,0:15:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.07,0:15:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結界…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.84,0:15:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三號樹 光是從三號樹那邊發出的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.00,0:15:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼搞的啊 在這種時候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.64,0:15:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了 來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.79,0:15:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼 光是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.44,0:15:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 被打開了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.54,0:15:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓧塚…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.26,0:16:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圓神大人的妖力…結界被…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.43,0:16:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只能用跑的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.31,0:16:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.87,0:16:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名 喂 秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.74,0:16:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人朝著元老院的方向奔去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.09,0:16:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.91,0:16:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.09,0:16:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之我和蒼先去元老院那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.23,0:16:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名你就去『七鄉』那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.67,0:16:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.40,0:16:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是結界被打開了 櫻花也綻放不了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.91,0:16:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀的靈魂仍然還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.94,0:16:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有何貴幹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.24,0:17:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是偶然進入了結界後而來到了這來逛逛的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.26,0:17:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土地神不是不介入人和妖怪之間的紛爭的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.82,0:17:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是這麼想的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.74,0:17:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土地神很中意這座城鎮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.85,0:17:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雄飛先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.11,0:17:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個傢伙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.65,0:17:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『針』
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.40,0:17:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為妖怪還真是半桶水啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.94,0:17:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 和我一樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.69,0:17:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…是半妖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.21,0:17:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.23,0:17:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.15,0:18:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他只是要逃到外面去了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.10,0:18:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事啊 這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.72,0:18:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.11,0:18:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.71,0:18:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.01,0:18:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀…銀…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.24,0:18:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.99,0:18:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.62,0:18:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我啊 是銀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.07,0:18:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比泉秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.59,0:18:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.32,0:18:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種表情是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.19,0:18:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微露出點笑容啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.98,0:18:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都兩年沒見了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.48,0:19:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.07,0:19:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圓神
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.23,0:19:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滾出去 從銀的體內滾出去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.23,0:19:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是很想那麼做的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.82,0:19:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是很遺憾 忘記了出來的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.13,0:19:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滾出去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.25,0:19:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 由你把我逼出來怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.32,0:19:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很容易吧 你的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.04,0:20:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收手的還真是時候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.96,0:20:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聰明的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.91,0:20:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事實也是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.87,0:20:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果把我送往那個世界的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.22,0:20:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個軀殼也會一同被送往那個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.11,0:20:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高興點吧 銀的靈魂依舊存在於這個軀殼內
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.14,0:20:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀…他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.79,0:20:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做了不少的抵抗 雖然是想把他給抹殺掉的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.57,0:20:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了如此地步變得更有趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.62,0:20:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.20,0:20:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手段還真是夠卑鄙的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.02,0:20:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自仗是土地神 就掉以輕心的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.83,0:20:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心馬失前蹄哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.45,0:20:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『春風』
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.33,0:21:08.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自以為是的可是你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.58,0:21:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.08,0:21:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見咯 秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.81,0:21:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.96,0:21:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有好好的在播放
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.60,0:21:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳聽到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.08,0:21:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳聽不清我也無能為力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.27,0:21:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.82,0:21:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼有沒有什麼事情發生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.10,0:21:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都沒有 一切太平
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.22,0:21:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣了 要掛咯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.38,0:21:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禮物的話就拜託…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.29,0:21:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣可以嗎 不跟她說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.62,0:22:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 也跟蒼保密
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.95,0:22:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.68,0:23:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是圓神
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.67,0:23:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是銀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.71,0:23:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合起來就是銀圓神
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.80,0:23:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這只有一個可以嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.92,0:23:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像這樣 用這橋段來博得暴笑如何
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.79,0:23:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人會笑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.41,0:23:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.04,0:23:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.98,0:23:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們來看看劇本吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.98,0:23:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰管它啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.06,0:23:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是這樣沒有人任何去照看
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.04,0:23:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人在一邊玩耍
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.27,0:24:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口才真不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.40,0:24:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣 下集夜櫻四重奏是講七海的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.24,0:24:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七海是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.67,0:24:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是不知道才讓人期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.31,0:24:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害 連大阪語也用上了
